Thank you so much for your kind words @NevilleSouthall ! I’m a big fan of @walesape & absolutely loved the privilege of being able to film Bili & Titch’s rescues. I cannot wait to see them both again & know the sanctuary must be struggling in the current climate! @CUBiosciences https://t.co/cFuGnz0fXW

We filmed both Bili & Titch’s rescues for #RhysJonesWildlifePatrol but now my friends at @walesape really do need your help to remain open! Here’s a link to their ‘Go Fund Me’ page, please help if you are able to, or consider retweeting if not, thank you!
